The,Wordsmith,API,is,an,instant,publishing,solution,for,a,variety,of,bulk,content,such,as,articles,blogs,and,reports,The,RESTful,API,functions,as,a,natural,language,generation,tool,that,uses,powerful,templates,to,convert,huge,volumes,of,data,into,text,without,compromising,the,uniqueness,of,each,piece,of,content,This,API,primarily,supports,HTTP,formatted,requests,and,returns,JSON,formatted,responses